IRS990.ActivityOrMissionDesc: The primary focus is to support the students and staff of the Allen Eagle Competitive Shooting Team. The organization is dedicated to supporting the team's student athletes through coordinating events fundraising grant scholarships and other related activities.

SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: The Organization has members but no stockholders. Each member has the same rights.
Members of the Organization elect members of the governing body.
The Board Officers receive a draft copy of Form 990 and approve it prior to its filing with the Internal Revenue Service.
Copies of the organizing documents are available to the general public upon request. The organization's financial statements are posted on the organization's website.
